
'''= Freimarkets is a protocol extension for bitcoin/freicoin that allows any user to issue his own assets or currencies among other new features'''


=Description=

"Freimarkets is a protocol extension for bitcoin/freicoin designed by [[Freicoin]] developers Mark Friedenbach and Jorge Timón that allows any user to issue his own assets or currencies among other new features like options, smart property or off-chain transactions for enhanced scalability. It is a hard-fork implementation of the general concept of colored coins. The funds collected will be used to implement the design in the link, but we reserve the right to make changes on the design as the technology demands."
(http://foundation.freicoin.org/#/donations/detail/20)


